Offers layers and frame-by-frame animation support for 2D sprite creation.
Features include color palette management, pixel-perfect editing, and onion skinning.
Time-saving features like tile mode and customizable brushes for repetitive patterns.
Exports sprite sheets, GIFs, and individual frames for easy integration.
Lightweight and fast, ideal for indie developers and artists.
A paid tool, but with a highly active community and frequent updates.

Website: https://www.aseprite.org
